results.name: Number of zeros in the period of Fibonacci 3-step sequence A000073 mod n.
link: T. D. Noe, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..1000
mathematica: n = 3; Table[a = Join[{1}, Table[0, {n - 1}]]; a = Mod[a, i]; a0 = a; k = 0; zeros = 0; While[k++; s = Mod[Plus @@ a, i]; a = RotateLeft[a]; If[s == 0, zeros++]; a[[n]] = s; a != a0]; zeros, {i, 100}]
results.author: _T. D. Noe_, Aug 18 2011
